arStrings.szText: Today, Master Elias called at my door. I had trouble with my words, so I showed him my carvings. He said he could see my pain in them. The pain of a lonely man who had learned to hate the world, and yet...
Hopeful. Emotional - Elias saw his suffering and gave him hope.
Our Mother, Lilith, found me beautiful. He said there are others like me as well, and together, we will build the new world.
